{"tid":2240422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[張五常攞獎未?] 兩學者改良拍賣理論 同獲諾貝爾經濟學獎","createTime":"2020-10-12T15:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T01:02:57.000Z","uid":213812,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb086654528aa0ad98660c51a59615803c3d4cc","tid":2240422,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"瑞典皇家科學院公布本年度諾貝爾最後一個獎項經濟學獎，由兩名美國經濟學家共同獲得，以表彰他們研究改良了拍賣理論及發明新的拍賣模式所作出的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n兩名獲獎者都是史丹福大學教授,，分別是72歲的米爾格龍 (Paul Milgrom)及83歲的威爾遜 (Robert B. Wilson)，兩人將分享1000萬瑞典克朗的獎金。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554286-20201012.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554286-20201012.htm&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=b1659f16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554286-20201012.htm&h=8f0219c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554286-20201012.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94gxFPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94gxFPc.jpg&h=30472f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">張五常係邊??徐家健係邊??</span>"},{"pid":"bc9095814ad36ad09450ce73e3c85dd0463657e7","tid":2240422,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:42:59.000Z","msg":"你在可處張五常?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d05b3d7fdb8454d6a6115d84b48707693bdd44","tid":2240422,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s